; Pinned for the contracts package. @types/chai is bumped to v5 here but
; @nomicfoundation/hardhat-toolbox@6.1.2 declares a peer dep on
; @types/chai@^4.2.0. Strict peer-dep resolution rejects the combo;
; legacy-peer-deps lets npm install both without erroring.
;
; Why this file exists (not just the CLI flag): the GitHub Actions
; crytic/slither-action runs inside its own Docker container which
; re-invokes `npm ci` WITHOUT passing --legacy-peer-deps. With this
; .npmrc in place every npm command in contracts/ — including the one
; inside Docker — picks up the flag automatically.
legacy-peer-deps=true
